{"tid":1540383,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"講個祕密大家知！（突發）","createTime":"2019-09-04T11:23:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T11:36:21.000Z","uid":310898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"870f3fb3717be3e185bd062a651d1cfb3f2548ce","tid":1540383,"uid":310898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:23:27.000Z","msg":"五大訴求、缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n點解依刻先突然講有機會撤回呀？<br />\n<br />\n因為佢地驚人權法案通過呀 大家9月8號記得要繼續出黎<br />\n我地係唔接受佢所謂善意。<br />\n善意代價 千幾手足被爆、7條命、幾隻眼？<br />\n<br />\n復會仲要10月1號後？<br />\n即係驚10月1號有事？大家要做好國際交宣了 <br />\n<br />\n我地唔可以懶呀 堅持呀各位 求下大家 堅持先見到希望<br />\n<br />\n我地要做到烈士、義士們既心願。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港、時代革命"},{"pid":"d5aa0258e4821a30f59c8707d0fa0631faa984a1","tid":1540383,"uid":310898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:26:40.000Z","msg":"推呀，屌"},{"pid":"b8d07a258890bdb3eb5e25027c6ddc1a68135c80","tid":1540383,"uid":310898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:29:41.000Z","msg":"推爆佢呀"},{"pid":"58003bb8a50a2aca261a73577ddcbcdfc794d116","tid":1540383,"uid":310898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:30:06.000Z","msg":"自推10連 幫手集氣"},{"pid":"73256eb092ea5a87f0f6b5fee61cea869c053f7f","tid":1540383,"uid":310898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:30:23.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"1bfed88dcd89a9b52de4b5612d5a4979d6c26f28","tid":1540383,"uid":310898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:30:35.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"16d0627602f263413d224efe73b07aa677514b02","tid":1540383,"uid":310898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:30:49.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"18557382740097ae2cf3b4d0346eb8ecf4536008","tid":1540383,"uid":310898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:31:04.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"053d127161e643a7b995cd88d2963d96f907bebd","tid":1540383,"uid":310898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09